        <h3><a href="#46-2d-位置" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-46-2d-位置"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>4.6 2D 位置</h3>
        <h4><a href="#强制-必须同时给出水平和垂直方向的位置" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-必须同时给出水平和垂直方向的位置"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] 必须同时给出水平和垂直方向的位置。</h4>
        <p>解释：</p>
        <p>2D 位置初始值为 <code>0% 0%</code>，但在只有一个方向的值时，另一个方向的值会被解析为 center。为避免理解上的困扰，应同时给出两个方向的值。<a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/colors.html#propdef-background-position" rel="nofollow">background-position属性值的定义</a></p>
        <p>示例：</p>
        <div class="highlight highlight-source-css"><pre><span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> good <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-ent">body</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">background-position</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">center</span> <span class="pl-c1">top</span>; <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> 50% 0% <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
}

<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> bad <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-ent">body</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">background-position</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">top</span>; <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> 50% 0% <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
}</pre></div>
        <h2><a href="#5-文本编排" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-5-文本编排"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>5 文本编排</h2>
        <h3><a href="#51-字体族" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-51-字体族"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>5.1 字体族</h3>
        <h4><a href="#强制-font-family-属性中的字体族名称应使用字体的英文-family-name其中如有空格须放置在引号中" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-font-family-属性中的字体族名称应使用字体的英文-family-name其中如有空格须放置在引号中"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] <code>font-family</code> 属性中的字体族名称应使用字体的英文 <code>Family Name</code>，其中如有空格，须放置在引号中。</h4>
