}

<span class="pl-ent">h1</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">font-family</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">Arial</span>, <span class="pl-s"><span class="pl-pds">"</span>Microsoft YaHei<span class="pl-pds">"</span></span>, <span class="pl-c1">sans-serif</span>;
}</pre></div>
        <h3><a href="#52-字号" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-52-字号"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>5.2 字号</h3>
        <h4><a href="#强制-需要在-windows-平台显示的中文内容其字号应不小于-12px" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-需要在-windows-平台显示的中文内容其字号应不小于-12px"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] 需要在 Windows 平台显示的中文内容，其字号应不小于 <code>12px</code>。</h4>
        <p>解释：</p>
        <p>由于 Windows 的字体渲染机制，小于 <code>12px</code> 的文字显示效果极差、难以辨认。</p>
        <h3><a href="#53-字体风格" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-53-字体风格"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>5.3 字体风格</h3>
        <h4><a href="#建议-需要在-windows-平台显示的中文内容不要使用除-normal-外的-font-style其他平台也应慎用" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-建议-需要在-windows-平台显示的中文内容不要使用除-normal-外的-font-style其他平台也应慎用"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[建议] 需要在 Windows 平台显示的中文内容，不要使用除 <code>normal</code> 外的 <code>font-style</code>。其他平台也应慎用。</h4>
        <p>解释：</p>
        <p>由于中文字体没有 <code>italic</code> 风格的实现，所有浏览器下都会 fallback 到 <code>obilique</code> 实现 (自动拟合为斜体)，小字号下 (特别是 Windows 下会在小字号下使用点阵字体的情况下) 显示效果差，造成阅读困难。</p>
        <h3><a href="#54-字重" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-54-字重"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>5.4 字重</h3>
        <h4><a href="#强制-font-weight-属性必须使用数值方式描述" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-font-weight-属性必须使用数值方式描述"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] <code>font-weight</code> 属性必须使用数值方式描述。</h4>
        <p>解释：</p>
        <p>CSS 的字重分 100 – 900 共九档，但目前受字体本身质量和浏览器的限制，实际上支持 <code>400</code> 和 <code>700</code> 两档，分别等价于关键词 <code>normal</code> 和 <code>bold</code>。</p>
        <p>浏览器本身使用一系列<a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/fonts.html#propdef-font-weight" rel="nofollow">启发式规则</a>来进行匹配，在 <code>&lt;700</code> 时一般匹配字体的 Regular 字重，<code>&gt;=700</code> 时匹配 Bold 字重。</p>
        <p>但已有浏览器开始支持 <code>=600</code> 时匹配 Semibold 字重 (见<a href="http://justineo.github.io/slideshows/font/#/3/15" rel="nofollow">此表</a>)，故使用数值描述增加了灵活性，也更简短。</p>
        <p>示例：</p>
        <div class="highlight highlight-source-css"><pre><span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> good <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-ent">h1</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">font-weight</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">700</span>;
}

<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> bad <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-ent">h1</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">font-weight</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">bold</span>;
}</pre></div>
        <h3><a href="#55-行高" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-55-行高"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>5.5 行高</h3>
        <h4><a href="#建议-line-height-在定义文本段落时应使用数值" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-建议-line-height-在定义文本段落时应使用数值"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[建议] <code>line-height</code> 在定义文本段落时，应使用数值。</h4>
        <p>解释：</p>
        <p>将 <code>line-height</code> 设置为数值，浏览器会基于当前元素设置的 <code>font-size</code> 进行再次计算。在不同字号的文本段落组合中，能达到较为舒适的行间间隔效果，避免在每个设置了 <code>font-size</code> 都需要设置 <code>line-height</code>。</p>
        <p>当 <code>line-height</code> 用于控制垂直居中时，还是应该设置成与容器高度一致。</p>
        <p>示例：</p>
        <div class="highlight highlight-source-css"><pre><span class="pl-e">.container</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">line-height</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">1.5</span>;
}</pre></div>
        <h2><a href="#6-变换与动画" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-6-变换与动画"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>6 变换与动画</h2>
        <h4><a href="#强制-使用-transition-时应指定-transition-property" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-使用-transition-时应指定-transition-property"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] 使用 <code>transition</code> 时应指定 <code>transition-property</code>。</h4>
        <p>示例：</p>
        <div class="highlight highlight-source-css"><pre><span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> good <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-e">.box</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">transition</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">color</span> <span class="pl-c1">1<span class="pl-k">s</span></span>, border-color <span class="pl-c1">1<span class="pl-k">s</span></span>;
}

<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> bad <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-e">.box</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">transition</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">all</span> <span class="pl-c1">1<span class="pl-k">s</span></span>;
}</pre></div>
        <h4><a href="#建议-尽可能在浏览器能高效实现的属性上添加过渡和动画" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-建议-尽可能在浏览器能高效实现的属性上添加过渡和动画"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[建议] 尽可能在浏览器能高效实现的属性上添加过渡和动画。</h4>
        <p>解释：</p>
        <p>见<a href="http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/speed/high-performance-animations/" rel="nofollow">本文</a>，在可能的情况下应选择这样四种变换：</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>transform: translate(npx, npx);</code></li>
            <li><code>transform: scale(n);</code></li>
            <li><code>transform: rotate(ndeg);</code></li>
            <li><code>opacity: 0..1;</code></li>
        </ul>
        <p>典型的，可以使用 <code>translate</code> 来代替 <code>left</code> 作为动画属性。</p>
        <p>示例：</p>
        <div class="highlight highlight-source-css"><pre><span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> good <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-e">.box</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">transition</span></span>: transform <span class="pl-c1">1<span class="pl-k">s</span></span>;
}
<span class="pl-e">.box</span><span class="pl-e">:hover</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">transform</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">translate</span>(<span class="pl-c1">20<span class="pl-k">px</span></span>); <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> move right for 20px <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
}

<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> bad <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-e">.box</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">left</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">0</span>;
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">transition</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">left</span> <span class="pl-c1">1<span class="pl-k">s</span></span>;
}
<span class="pl-e">.box</span><span class="pl-e">:hover</span> {
    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">left</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">20<span class="pl-k">px</span></span>; <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> move right for 20px <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
}</pre></div>
        <h2><a href="#7-响应式" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-7-响应式"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>7 响应式</h2>
        <h4><a href="#强制-media-query-不得单独编排必须与相关的规则一起定义" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-media-query-不得单独编排必须与相关的规则一起定义"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] <code>Media Query</code> 不得单独编排，必须与相关的规则一起定义。</h4>
        <p>示例：</p>
        <div class="highlight highlight-source-css"><pre><span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> Good <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> header styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-k">@media</span> (...) {
    <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> header styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
}

<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> main styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-k">@media</span> (...) {
    <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> main styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
}

<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> footer styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-k">@media</span> (...) {
    <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> footer styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
}


<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> Bad <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> header styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> main styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> footer styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>

<span class="pl-k">@media</span> (...) {
    <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> header styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
    <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> main styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
    <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> footer styles <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
}</pre></div>
        <h4><a href="#强制-media-query-如果有多个逗号分隔的条件时应将每个条件放在单独一行中" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-media-query-如果有多个逗号分隔的条件时应将每个条件放在单独一行中"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] <code>Media Query</code> 如果有多个逗号分隔的条件时，应将每个条件放在单独一行中。</h4>
        <p>示例：</p>
        <div class="highlight highlight-source-css"><pre><span class="pl-k">@media</span>
(<span class="pl-c1">-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio</span>: <span class="pl-c1">2</span>), <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> Webkit-based browsers <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
(min--moz-device-pixel-ratio: <span class="pl-c1">2</span>),    <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> Older Firefox browsers (prior to Firefox 16) <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
(<span class="pl-c1">min-resolution</span>: <span class="pl-c1">2<span class="pl-k">dppx</span></span>),             <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> The standard way <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
(<span class="pl-c1">min-resolution</span>: <span class="pl-c1">192<span class="pl-k">dpi</span></span>) {           <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> dppx fallback <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
    <span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">/*</span> Retina-specific stuff here <span class="pl-c">*/</span></span>
